                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "review",
            "text": "Review the CSV for gaps, spikes >2\u00b0C/hour, or flatline sensor faults. Classify healthy vs anomaly before charting.",
            "options": [
